Day 62: Manage Secrets in Kubernetes

Date: October 30, 2025
Overview
Secured sensitive data using Kubernetes Secrets.
Key Concepts Learned

Secret types
Base64 encoding
Secret injection methods
Security best practices

Commands Used
bashkubectl create secret generic db-secret --from-literal=password=mypassword
kubectl get secrets
kubectl describe secret db-secret
Challenges Faced
Understanding that base64 is encoding, not encryption! Real security requires additional measures.
